<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 9 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 2,547.61 on Saturday, up 2.41
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 13,015,057 shares changed hands in 2,006 deals and
the turnover stood at 89.49 billion rials (about 29.83 million U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
Sixty issues registered gains while 32 others declined. 
