Pakistan, saying that his country will continue to develop still
closer cooperation with China.
</P>
<P>
Musharaf invited President Jiang to pay an official visit to
Pakistan, and Jiang accepted the invitation with pleasure.
</P>
<P>
Jiang and Musharaf arrived in New York to attend the
Millennium Summit, which ended Friday at the U.N. headquarters.
</P>
</TEXT>
