Minister of Health Zhang Wenkang and Fernando Chui Sai On,
secretary for social and cultural affairs of the Macao SAR
government, authorized the agreements.
</P>
<P>
Fernando Chui said that Macao has received medical assistance
from the inland areas over the past years and more medical
specialists will be invited to work in Macao.  
