<HEADLINE> Pakistan Works Towards being Opium-Free by December 2000 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Interior Minister
Moinuddin Haider said on Friday that all possible measures are
being taken to eliminate narcotics and to make Pakistan a opium-
